---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="European Union | ARM Management"
  description="ARM Management advises on company formation, accounting, payroll, global mobility, and transaction advisory across all 27 EU member states plus UK and Switzerland."
>
<main>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1467269204594-9661b134dd2b?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">EU Region</span>
      <h1>European Union</h1>
      <p>All 27 EU member states plus UK and Switzerland.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Overview</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">ARM Management in European Union</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">ARM Management has operated across the European Union since the firm's founding. We advise on company formation across all 27 member states plus the UK and Switzerland, coordinate VAT and corporate tax compliance, manage payroll across EU jurisdictions, and handle EU Golden Visa residency applications for investors seeking EU residency rights.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:20px">The EU represents the world's largest single market with harmonised regulatory frameworks across member states — but significant local variations in tax, employment law, and corporate governance requirements. ARM Management navigates this complexity on behalf of clients, coordinating all local advisors through a single senior relationship.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--warm" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Services in European Union</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">What ARM Management Does Here</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal" style="color:#6B7280;margin-bottom:40px">All six ARM practice areas are available across the European Union. Click any service to learn more.</p>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <a href="/services/transaction-advisory" class="card reveal reveal-delay-1" style="text-decoration:none;display:block"><h3>Transaction Advisory</h3><p>Cross-border M&amp;A, private investment, and deal structuring across EU member states and the UK.</p><span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span></a>
        <a href="/services/company-formation"    class="card reveal reveal-delay-2" style="text-decoration:none;display:block"><h3>Company Formation</h3><p>Legal entity incorporation across EU jurisdictions including UK, Netherlands, Germany, Malta, Lithuania, and Switzerland.</p><span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span></a>
        <a href="/services/accounting-tax"       class="card reveal reveal-delay-3" style="text-decoration:none;display:block"><h3>Accounting &amp; Tax</h3><p>Monthly bookkeeping, VAT returns, corporate tax filings, and annual accounts across EU jurisdictions.</p><span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span></a>
        <a href="/services/payroll-hr"           class="card reveal reveal-delay-1" style="text-decoration:none;display:block"><h3>Payroll &amp; HR</h3><p>Multi-country payroll compliance, employment contract advisory, and HR compliance across EU member states.</p><span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span></a>
        <a href="/services/global-mobility"      class="card reveal reveal-delay-2" style="text-decoration:none;display:block"><h3>Global Mobility</h3><p>EU Golden Visa programmes including Greece, Portugal, Malta, and Spain. Schengen residency for investors.</p><span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span></a>
        <a href="/services/crypto-web3"          class="card reveal reveal-delay-3" style="text-decoration:none;display:block"><h3>Crypto &amp; Web3</h3><p>MiCA CASP authorisation across Malta, Lithuania, Ireland, and other EU member states. Full EU crypto compliance.</p><span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="reveal">Begin Your European Union Expansion</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Speak with a senior ARM advisor about your requirements in the European Union. We will give you an honest assessment of what is achievable, on what timeline, and at what cost.</p>
    <div class="btn-row reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</Base>
